News.Title: Pritika Engineering Secures ₹70 Crore Contract from Material Handling Equipment Manufacturer
News.Summary: Pritika Engineering has secured a contract worth approximately ₹70 crore from a material handling equipment manufacturer. The contract represents a significant business win for the company.

News.Title: Pritika Engineering Secures ₹50 Crore Order from Major MNC Tractor Manufacturer
News.Summary: Pritika Engineering has finalized an order worth approximately ₹50 crore from a leading multinational corporation (MNC) that manufactures tractors. This significant order represents a major business development for the company.
